    },
    {
      "id": "VOmnHL7UaAKS5JUy4FYjt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 450.39996337890625,
      "y": 452.18121337890625,
      "width": 785.45947265625,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 920752025,
      "version": 432,
      "versionNonce": 524007417,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777054447876,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Function Requirements ( Core Main feature/Functionality )\n    1. User should be able to create/update/delete documents.\n    2. Multiple users can edit the same document simultaneously.\n    3. User should be able to view each other's changes in real-time.\n    4. User should be able to see the cursor position and presence of other user\n    5. Documents must support versioning.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Function Requirements ( Core Main feature/Functionality )\n    1. User should be able to create/update/delete documents.\n    2. Multiple users can edit the same document simultaneously.\n    3. User should be able to view each other's changes in real-time.\n    4. User should be able to see the cursor position and presence of other user\n    5. Documents must support versioning.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "cvc05BQwlsCglj4P665zc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 430.5999755859375,
      "y": 656.78125,
      "width": 836.6393432617188,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1329645143,
      "version": 516,
      "versionNonce": 1329628345,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777054622376,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Non-Functional Requirements ( System Behaviour / PErfromance )\n    1. Scale: Millions of users, with some billions of documents in database.\n    2. CAP Theorm: Availability > Consistency \n        - So when multiple users collaborate, the system should be available to \n          all users.\n        - A slight delay in seeing the changes of other user is acceptable in this case. \n    3. Latency: Updates should be low latency ~ 100 ms.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Non-Functional Requirements ( System Behaviour / PErfromance )\n    1. Scale: Millions of users, with some billions of documents in database.\n    2. CAP Theorm: Availability > Consistency \n        - So when multiple users collaborate, the system should be available to \n          all users.\n        - A slight delay in seeing the changes of other user is acceptable in this case. \n    3. Latency: Updates should be low latency ~ 100 ms.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "JEedUqAs4lXEhaHAQpswT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1465.7334662543403,
      "y": 416.2937757703993,
      "width": 209.49986267089844,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1593608887,
      "version": 157,
      "versionNonce": 761149175,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777055021360,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core Entities:\n    - Users / Editors.\n    - Document\n    - Cursor.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Entities:\n    - Users / Editors.\n    - Document\n    - Cursor.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "f-KA5JmUy79QqnaXLeI3z",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1462.333468967014,
      "y": 564.9166734483506,
      "width": 879.4193115234375,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1690284919,
      "version": 606,
      "versionNonce": 292508569,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777055031544,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API Designing:\n\n1. Handle Documents creation & Management\n    \n    POST:  /v1/api/docs/create - create a document (Returns Id)\n    \n    GET:   /v1/api/docs/{docsId}  - View document (Read only mode)\n    \n        ... Other CRUD API to manage document.\n\n2. Editing a Document - can be alone or with other users. - [ use websocket Connection ]\n\n    WS: /v1/api/docs/{docId} - Edit document",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API Designing:\n\n1. Handle Documents creation & Management\n    \n    POST:  /v1/api/docs/create - create a document (Returns Id)\n    \n    GET:   /v1/api/docs/{docsId}  - View document (Read only mode)\n    \n        ... Other CRUD API to manage document.\n\n2. Editing a Document - can be alone or with other users. - [ use websocket Connection ]\n\n    WS: /v1/api/docs/{docId} - Edit document",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
